  "texts": [
    "Many respondents emphasized that ChatGPT should be used primarily for brainstorming and idea generation, with a cautionary note that fact-checking is crucial for the content it generates.",
    "All survey results based on a 5-point Likert scale are summarized in Figure 4.",
    "In contradiction to the findings of Ngo (2023), we found that the mean value (2.81) of the negative aspects are not as important to students compared to the mean value (3.45) of the positive aspects and the mean value (3.49) of the general aspects.",
    "Therefore, in our study, the positive aspects outweigh the negative aspects, while the mean value (3.64) of barriers in Ngo (2023) on using ChatGPT are slightly higher than the mean value (3.58) on benefits of using it.",
    "Our survey on students' user experience of ChatGPT revealed several key insights."
